WEBVTT

00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:45.250
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:51.666 --> 00:00:53.583
Back in the days in Chang'an,

00:00:53.625 --> 00:00:55.416
there wasn't a single young lady who wasn't afraid of me.

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:56.875
No matter what,

00:00:56.958 --> 00:00:59.708
you must come out before the candle goes out.

00:00:59.791 --> 00:01:01.250
Do you understand?

00:01:31.875 --> 00:01:33.500
My little beauty

00:01:39.666 --> 00:01:40.625
Let me go

00:01:54.333 --> 00:01:56.458
Brothel keeper, bring me ten more candles

00:02:00.708 --> 00:02:01.708
Where is everyone?

00:02:29.083 --> 00:02:30.250
Help!

00:02:30.833 --> 00:02:32.916
Don’t you like to play?

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:35.000
Then let’s play together

00:02:35.250 --> 00:02:36.458
I don’t want to anymore

00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:37.041
Help!

00:02:53.208 --> 00:02:55.166
The body is heavy and bloodless

00:02:55.708 --> 00:02:57.333
The eyes are lifeless and vacant

00:02:58.125 --> 00:02:59.375
Looks like his life force is drained

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:02.083
Although Xun Wan is the eldest son of the Imperial Secretary

00:03:02.166 --> 00:03:03.833
He’s known for his lustful ways

00:03:03.958 --> 00:03:05.000
Back in Chang’an

00:03:05.041 --> 00:03:07.083
He was a regular at several brothels and taverns

00:03:07.125 --> 00:03:10.166
The Imperial Secretary sent a letter asking me to investigate

00:03:10.250 --> 00:03:11.666
Probably doesn’t want the scandal to spread

00:03:11.708 --> 00:03:13.875
Boss, I’ve heard elders say

00:03:13.958 --> 00:03:15.458
Excessive yang attracts lustful ghosts

00:03:15.541 --> 00:03:17.166
The way he died

00:03:17.458 --> 00:03:19.791
He was likely killed by a ghost courtesan

00:03:23.250 --> 00:03:24.000
Ghost courtesan

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:24.666
Yes

00:03:24.750 --> 00:03:27.541
The last place Xun Wan was seen was Liuxiang Pavilion

00:03:27.625 --> 00:03:30.500
It’s said Liuxiang Pavilion has an unwritten rule

00:03:30.541 --> 00:03:32.166
It only opens at midnight

00:03:33.416 --> 00:03:35.541
Legend says it’s connected to the underworld

00:03:35.625 --> 00:03:38.041
Even ghost courtesans come out to serve guests

00:03:39.541 --> 00:03:41.750
Boss, it took me a lot of effort to find that place

00:03:41.833 --> 00:03:43.083
Time is tight

00:03:43.125 --> 00:03:44.250
Go back to Chang’an and report first

00:03:44.333 --> 00:03:45.458
I’ll follow soon

00:03:45.541 --> 00:03:47.750
Remember, don’t spread word of this case

00:03:47.833 --> 00:03:48.958
Yes, boss

00:04:05.125 --> 00:04:06.125
Where’s Lin Xiaoran?

00:04:06.541 --> 00:04:08.541
What, are you afraid he’ll run away?

00:04:09.375 --> 00:04:12.958
Lin Xiaoran, you still owe me payment

00:04:13.625 --> 00:04:15.708
I’m so poor, all I have left is my good looks

00:04:15.833 --> 00:04:16.875
Give me a little more time

00:04:18.166 --> 00:04:19.208
Lin Xiaoran

00:04:19.750 --> 00:04:21.708
You dare attack a court official?

00:04:22.416 --> 00:04:23.333
Lord Li

00:04:23.791 --> 00:04:25.208
It was this heroine who did it

00:04:25.291 --> 00:04:26.125
You

00:04:29.208 --> 00:04:30.416
May I ask your name, heroine?

00:04:31.125 --> 00:04:32.500
I am Shen Qiuwan

00:04:32.833 --> 00:04:33.958
He told me to do it

00:04:34.208 --> 00:04:35.666
He owes me money and won’t pay

00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:36.666
Lin Xiaoran

00:04:37.333 --> 00:04:38.916
I think you have a talent for solving cases

00:04:39.208 --> 00:04:41.250
Why not join me in the Cold Case Bureau?

00:04:41.416 --> 00:04:43.541
I’ll help pay your debt

00:04:43.666 --> 00:04:44.916
I don’t want to pay

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:45.583
You

00:04:45.583 --> 00:04:46.750
That’s not up to you

00:04:48.666 --> 00:04:49.958
Alright, alright, alright

00:04:50.750 --> 00:04:52.333
Great, I found someone to help pay my debt

00:04:52.375 --> 00:04:54.208
Perfect, I’ll join the Cold Case Bureau

00:04:55.625 --> 00:04:58.333
With you here, he can’t escape

00:05:00.958 --> 00:05:04.833
At the hour of Zi, the gates to the underworld open

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:11.833
Honored guests

00:05:11.833 --> 00:05:14.750
Tonight’s auction will begin soon

00:05:14.916 --> 00:05:18.291
As always, highest bidder wins

00:05:20.250 --> 00:05:22.750
Wow, so beautiful

00:05:23.583 --> 00:05:25.041
Really nice, look

00:05:53.041 --> 00:05:53.916
Good

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.166
Shen Qiuwan

00:05:55.250 --> 00:05:56.583
You keep watch here

00:05:56.791 --> 00:05:58.041
I’ll go upstairs to look for clues

00:05:58.083 --> 00:05:58.791
Hey

00:05:59.666 --> 00:06:01.166
The bill isn’t settled yet, Lord Li

00:06:01.208 --> 00:06:03.208
You’re really stuck with Lin Xiaoran

00:06:04.125 --> 00:06:04.916
Brothel keeper

00:06:05.291 --> 00:06:06.041
Yes

00:06:06.625 --> 00:06:07.291
Lead the way

00:06:07.375 --> 00:06:08.666
Alright, this way please

00:06:09.375 --> 00:06:10.541
Thanks

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.583
Wow, such a great dance

00:06:21.666 --> 00:06:22.583
Good

00:06:23.208 --> 00:06:24.416
Excellent

00:06:27.750 --> 00:06:31.666
Miss Wannin is one of Liuxiang Pavilion’s most popular girls

00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:34.250
Starting price is one thousand taels

00:06:36.541 --> 00:06:38.125
Three thousand taels

00:06:38.208 --> 00:06:40.208
Wow, Wannin

00:06:40.291 --> 00:06:42.875
You were auctioned for three thousand taels of gold

00:06:42.916 --> 00:06:45.416
Ten times higher than the other girls

00:06:46.458 --> 00:06:48.291
Can they compare to me?

00:06:48.375 --> 00:06:50.083
A bunch of worthless fools

00:06:52.125 --> 00:06:53.583
What are you so proud of?

00:06:54.333 --> 00:06:56.833
Everything you have was given by me

00:06:57.666 --> 00:06:59.541
You’d better know your place

00:07:00.125 --> 00:07:01.000
Go

00:07:01.291 --> 00:07:03.166
Bring the guest over

00:07:17.083 --> 00:07:19.166
On this guest register

00:07:19.458 --> 00:07:21.333
Why isn’t Xun Wan’s name listed?

00:07:52.916 --> 00:07:53.916
Lord Li

00:07:55.041 --> 00:07:55.958
What's wrong?

00:07:57.833 --> 00:07:58.875
Where is he?

00:08:00.375 --> 00:08:01.791
Who?

00:08:05.375 --> 00:08:06.458
Where's Lin Xiaoran?

00:08:06.875 --> 00:08:07.833
I don't know.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.875
He said there are ghosts in Liuxiang Pavilion.

00:08:14.583 --> 00:08:15.916
His Three Pure Bells rang.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.083
That didn't happen.

00:08:17.583 --> 00:08:19.916
But take a good sniff.

00:08:20.083 --> 00:08:23.125
Besides wine, lust, and money, what else is here?

00:08:32.583 --> 00:08:33.583
What's going on?

00:08:34.375 --> 00:08:37.666
This guest won Miss Wannin with a bid of three thousand taels.

00:08:37.791 --> 00:08:39.583
So I sent Wannin to serve him.

00:08:39.625 --> 00:08:42.416
But who could've expected this to happen?

00:08:47.041 --> 00:08:49.291
Zhang Can from Luoyang Protectorate

00:08:50.041 --> 00:08:52.125
Committed suicide two years ago out of guilt.

00:08:54.208 --> 00:08:56.125
It seems those who come here for pleasure

00:08:56.708 --> 00:08:59.916
are all ghosts who dare not seek joy in daylight.

00:09:10.583 --> 00:09:11.958
If that's the case,

00:09:12.833 --> 00:09:13.958
these two

00:09:15.333 --> 00:09:17.000
don't seem like something humans did.

00:09:18.958 --> 00:09:20.791
The girls all say there are ghosts in the building.

00:09:20.791 --> 00:09:22.041
I didn't believe it.

00:09:22.125 --> 00:09:24.000
But I didn't expect it to be true.

00:09:29.875 --> 00:09:31.333
Li Jingnian from the Cold Case Bureau

00:09:31.458 --> 00:09:34.708
From now on, Liuxiang Pavilion is sealed off.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.625
No one is allowed in or out.

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:37.666
Lord Li

00:09:37.750 --> 00:09:39.875
What should we do next?

00:09:40.041 --> 00:09:41.541
At the third quarter of the hour of Zi

00:09:41.708 --> 00:09:42.833
Break the rules

00:09:43.166 --> 00:09:44.625
Catch the evil ghost